Package de.fhb.sailboat.control.navigator

Interface Summary
Navigator Interface for executing a Task.
 

Class Summary
BeatWorker Implements a beat behavior.
NavigatorImpl Implementation of Navigator which calculates commands based on the Task to execute.
ReachCircleWorker Calculates the relative angle from the current position to the goal defined in the task to execute and hands it over to the pilot.
ReachPolygonWorker Calculates the relative angle from the current position to the centroid of the polygon defined in the task to be executed and hands it over to the pilot.
WorkerThread<T extends Task> Base class for navigation threads.
